# Privacy Policy for GlowCompare AI Selfie Tracker
**Last Updated: July 9, 2026**
Dhinova Tech ("we," "our," or "us") operates the **GlowCompare AI Selfie Tracker** mobile application (the "App"). We are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our App. 
Please read this Privacy Policy carefully. By using the App, you consent to the data practices described in this policy.
---
## 1. Local-First Data Philosophy & Security
GlowCompare is built with a **local-first** approach. This means:
*   **Local Storage**: All selfies, photo logs, routine checklists, product shelf details, and skincare logs are stored **100% locally** on your device. We do not host, store, or view your photos or database records on our own servers.
*   **Google Drive Sync (Optional)**: If you choose to enable the cloud backup feature, the App will prompt you to link your Google Account. Backup files are securely uploaded directly from your device to your personal Google Drive storage (using the secure `drive.appdata` scope, which isolates the App's data from the rest of your Drive). Dhinova Tech has no access to your Google Account credentials or any files stored in your Google Drive.
*   **AI Analysis (Optional)**: If you use the AI analysis features (such as scanning routine products or analyzing skin milestones), the App utilizes Google's **Gemini API (Paid Tier)**. 
    *   *AI Data Protection*: We use the enterprise/paid tier of the Gemini API. Google guarantees that data (including photos and text) sent via this API tier is **never used to train Google's AI models** and is processed securely.
---
## 2. Information We Collect and How We Use It
To provide the App's features, we require access to certain device permissions and capabilities:
### A. Device Permissions
*   **Camera (`android.permission.CAMERA`)**: Used to capture progress selfies and scan product barcodes. Photos are stored locally and are not transmitted to us.
*   **Storage & Media Access (`READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE`, `WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE`, `READ_MEDIA_IMAGES`)**: Used to save, retrieve, and view progress selfies and comparison images on your device.
*   **Biometrics (`android.permission.USE_BIOMETRIC`)**: Used for the optional biometric lock feature to secure your private photo logs. Authentication is handled entirely by your device’s operating system; we never receive or store your biometric credentials.
*   **Notifications & Alarms (`POST_NOTIFICATIONS`, `SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM`, `RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED`)**: Used to send you reminders for your scheduled skincare routines.
*   **Network & Internet (`INTERNET`, `ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE`)**: Required to fetch ads from AdMob, communicate with the Gemini API for skincare analysis, and perform Google Drive backup sync.
*   **Wake Lock (`WAKE_LOCK`)**: Used to ensure routine alarms trigger reliably even when the device is asleep.
### B. Third-Party Service Providers
The App integrates third-party services that may collect information used to identify you. Below are links to the privacy policies of the third-party service providers used by the App:
*   **Google Play Services**: [https://policies.google.com/privacy](https://policies.google.com/privacy)
*   **Google AdMob (Ads)**: [https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads](https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads)
*   **Google Gemini API**: [https://ai.google.dev/terms/api-terms](https://ai.google.dev/terms/api-terms)
